<h4 id="installingalocalserver">Installing a Local Server</h4>

<p>First things first, you'll need to install Ruby 2.5.0. I recommend using the excellent <a href="https://github.com/rbenv/rbenv">rbenv</a>,
and <a href="https://github.com/rbenv/ruby-build">ruby-build</a></p>

<pre><code class="bash language-bash">rbenv install 2.5.0
rbenv global 2.5.0
</code></pre>

